OL,3,CMan, 48, jailed after brutal attack
OL,4,Cand rape of woman
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for the brutal
OL,7,Fattack and rape of a woman in County
OL,8,FDurham.
OL,10,FMark Taylor assaulted the woman while
OL,11,Fthe pair were socialising at his
OL,12,Fformer home in Front Street, Shotton
OL,13,FColliery, in December 2023.
OL,15,FThe 48-year-old dragged the woman to
OL,16,Fthe floor, hit her repeatedly in the
OL,17,Fface and then raped her, in an attack
OL,18,Flasting around 20 minutes.
