OL,6,FThe woman fled the house after Taylor
OL,7,Ffell asleep, and contacted a family
OL,8,Fmember who then called the police.
OL,10,FOfficers attended the scene where they
OL,11,Farrested Taylor, and an investigation
OL,12,Fwas launched.
OL,14,FHe was subsequently charged with rape,
OL,15,Fsexual assault, and assault
OL,16,Foccasioning actual bodily harm.
OL,18,FTaylor denied rape and sexual assault,
OL,19,Fbut pleaded guilty to assault at the
OL,20,Fstart of his trial at Durham Crown
OL,21,FCourt last month.
