OL,7,Fmy best to clean the painful memories
OL,8,Faway. Despite how much I try, I still
OL,9,Ffeel dirty.
OL,11,F"I can't eat or sleep properly ` I'm
OL,12,Fhaving nightmares reliving what has
OL,13,Fhappened to me. I just want these
OL,14,Fpainful memories and feelings to go
OL,15,Faway. I want to be me again."
