OL,6,FDetective Constable Adam Abram, from
OL,7,FDurham Constabulary, who led the
OL,8,Finvestigation, said:"The courage and
OL,9,Fstrength shown by the woman has been
OL,10,Ftruly commendable - her support for
OL,11,Four investigation has resulted in
OL,12,FTaylor being put behind bars," he said.
OL,14,F"While today's sentencing will not
OL,15,Ftake away the pain or the memories of
OL,16,Fwhat happened, I hope it will enable
OL,17,Fher to start to move forward.
